ALG Enhanced AK trigger was installed. Barrel was threaded 1/2x28 to allow use with normal flash hiders or suppressors. Threads and barrel were checked for concentricity by the smith. Gas Piston and spring system were tuned to lower the gas pressure on the carrier (these are notoroiusly overgassed). This now runs 100% reliably both suppressed and unsupressed - rare feature for AK variants. The famous TWS Dogleg Rail cover as well as rear peep sight were installed. Finally, the Midwest Industries MLOK handgaurd installed (will also include the original wood front handgaurd). This "pistol" had a lot of care go into it and is an incredible project. Ton of fun to shoot. Will include 2 PMAGs and 2 factory mags with purchase to qualifying buyers. Must ship/transfer through FFL
